## Exsang Damage

When you cast `Exsanguinate`, displays the damage being done by your hastened
bleeds (`Rupture`, `Garrote`).

**Classes**: Rogue (Assassination)

**Requested by**: Zavinn

### Changes

#### v0.1 (2016-07-26):

Initial release.
